com.github.seqware.queryengine.system.importers
Class FeatureImporter

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.system.importers.Importer
      com.github.seqware.queryengine.system.importers.FeatureImporter

public class FeatureImporter
extends Importer

Port of the class from the original prototype, adapted to use the new classes in the new API; command-line interface is the older one without support for SO. In the old API, there was very little "management" code so all of the workers shared a reference to the same Store class with a small dab of synchronization. In the new API, we have to contend with the CreateUpdateManager, so I think it makes more sense to have one CreateUpdateManager per thread rather than freeze all threads when one wants to synchronize for example.
